title: Frank Lloyd Wright Coonley Playhouse Window Metal Bookmark
description:
This bookmark features a playful art glass window design created by Frank Lloyd Wright in 1912. With asymmetrical geometric designs and suggestions of flags, balloons, and confetti, the brightly colored windows bring to mind a parade—a fun theme and appropriate for a children's playroom.

Bookmark is packaged in a recycled PET plastic sleeve with provenance card.

  • Dimensions: 1.25 x 3.75 in.
  • Materials: Solid brass, electro-plated with hematite finish, giclée print
